  --- spring-boot-starter-quartz
  Stack Overflow Spring Boot Reference IO Quartz Scheduler Quartz Scheduler Spring Boot offers several conveniences for working with the Quartz scheduler , including the spring-boot-starter-quartz starter. If Quartz is available, a Scheduler is auto-configured (through the SchedulerFactoryBean abstraction). Beans of the following types are automatically picked up and associated with the Scheduler : JobDetail : defines a particular Job. JobDetail instances can be built with the JobBuilder API. <
  --- Quartz Scheduler
